Package com.pumaray.lib.javafx.view.control.action

Class PumAbstractFXAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pumaray.lib.javafx.view.control.action.PumAbstractFXAction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PumAction, PumFXAction, EventListener, javafx.event.EventHandler<javafx.event.ActionEvent>
    public abstract class PumAbstractFXAction
extends Object
implements PumFXAction
    Author:
    Pumaray Developer This class provides default implementations for the Pumaray FX Action. The developer need only subclass this abstract class and define the canDoAction and the doAction methods.
